QuestData.Title: I'm Saved!
QuestData.Description: I don't mind sharing. I'm just glad to be saved from that creep, Gankly! And I collected tons of skins from Zangarmarsh, so it's no problem at all!
QuestData.LogDescription: Give the Bundle of Skins to Harold Lane at the Nesingwary Safari in Nagrand.
QuestData.CompletionText: Kristen is a very nice...<cough>... person to share her skins, wouldn't you agree?
QuestData.RewardText: Well, I couldn't see if you helped out with saving Kristen, or not. But if she handed you one of her bundles of skins then you're alright in my book.Here's your reward.
